@echo off\n\n:: Define source and destination directories\nset SOURCE_DIR=C:\path\to\source\nset DEST_DIR=D:\path\to\destination\n\n:: Execute Robocopy to perform the backup\nrobocopy %SOURCE_DIR% %DEST_DIR% /MIR /R:3 /W:5 /Z /V /NP /LOG:C:\path\to\logfile.log\n\n:: Schedule the script to run at intervals using Task Scheduler\n:: Create a new task in Task Scheduler to run this script at desired intervals